{"tid":2063374,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[$100獎勵]發明除非你係警察既天才 西灣河開槍案","createTime":"2020-06-14T02:45:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T05:40:37.000Z","uid":220942,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2779f05b01d09e591f16a37ea400277cfb364282","tid":2063374,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T02:45:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">犯法就係犯法<br />\n除非你係警察</span></span><br />\n<br />\n發明呢句既一定係天才<br />\n律政司而家開明牌<br />\n話可以唔俾法官審西灣河開槍警察有冇犯法<br />\n所有想犯罪既人應該考慮做警察，因為律政司會包底<br />\n<br />\n如果有人proof到係佢作，我可以獎$100俾佢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n節錄now：<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=394123\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D394123&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJhR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=d36dd122\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D394123&h=3109f80b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=394123</a><br />\n<br />\n若律政司認為無合理定罪機會、違反公衆利益，或基於政治因素利用私人檢控，構成濫用司法程序，造成不公，律政司司長有責任介入，並停止相關法律程序，以維護公義。"},{"pid":"d145e655281fdfaed06d346737be732ba77c63ac","tid":2063374,"uid":343361,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T02:46:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">犯法就係犯法<br />\n除非你係警察</span></span>"},{"pid":"b35b858f079a58796c9cda3d69e7be1b21b3a75b","tid":2063374,"uid":262035,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T02:58:52.000Z","msg":"睇標題都唔知up乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e53ac3de7502524a11649b95dc40a8406ab26858","tid":2063374,"uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b35b858f079a58796c9cda3d69e7be1b21b3a75b",